are buzzing around me like flies...

544
00:37:05,200 --> 00:37:06,530
Done?

545
00:37:08,080 --> 00:37:11,240
Stop behaving like a spoilt child!

546
00:37:12,290 --> 00:37:14,030
Someone just snatched
your favourite toy!

547
00:37:14,120 --> 00:37:15,910
Your heart is just fine!

548
00:37:16,580 --> 00:37:18,780
What do you even
know about heartbreak!

549
00:37:19,160 --> 00:37:20,870
Sorry, only you know everything!

550
00:37:21,040 --> 00:37:21,910
Listen!

551
00:37:22,790 --> 00:37:24,950
