1504
02:04:04,700 --> 02:04:06,490
Love is like cancer.

1505
02:04:07,660 --> 02:04:09,530
Comes without warning...

1506
02:04:09,990 --> 02:04:11,990
...and destroys you in its wake.

1507
02:04:14,160 --> 02:04:16,450
This can't be happening, Alizeh...

1508
02:04:19,450 --> 02:04:22,780
Well... It's happened.

1509
02:04:28,490 --> 02:04:31,490
I thought I was so cool...

1510
02:04:33,200 --> 02:04:35,990
Love turned me
into such a loser.

1511
02:04:39,660 --> 02:04:42,330
Ali was making me act insane...

1512
02:04:42,740 --> 02:04:45,700
